data.description: In River Vista's highly sought-after community, this 2016-built home offers ocean access without fixed bridges. Situated on an oversized corner lot with beautiful landscaping, it features a 2018 dock, a 2020 boat lift, impact windows, Cambria quartz countertops, upgraded cabinets, and stainless appliances.    Inside, porcelain wood-look tile spans throughout. The garage has upgraded insulation and an epoxy floor. redone in 2023. Outdoors, a gas saltwater pool (2021), and a hot tub await. Enjoy a prime location near Club Med, Sandpiper Marina, and the Botanical Garden.    Low HOA fees make this property even more appealing. Recent additions include a 2022 EV charger, 2020 privacy fence, smart lock & thermostat, 2022 water well, 2021 firepit, and 2020 interior paint and light fixture updates Owner/Agent
